source:
TEXT_LUCKZG023_03508_SEQ_00<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var> Quest Sync<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>
Twine is in need of an extra pair of eyes. Namely, yours.
target:
TEXT_LUCKZG023_03508_SEQ_00<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var>特殊ルール： レベルアジャスト<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>
トゥワインの悩める労働者は、冒険者に点検を手伝ってほしいようだ。

source: TEXT_LUCKZG023_03508_TODO_00<tab>Inspect structures in need of repair.
target: TEXT_LUCKZG023_03508_TODO_00<tab>修理が必要な場所を調べる

source: TEXT_LUCKZG023_03508_MINER03508_000_000<tab>Gods! This whole place is falling apart! My job is to order materials for repairs, but the budget is so tight I can't afford to buy more than is absolutely necessary.
target:
TEXT_LUCKZG023_03508_MINER03508_000_000<tab>近々、モルド族の行商人が訪れるので、
壊れた建物を修理するための資材を発注しようと思う。
だが、余分な資材を買うだけの金銭的な余裕はない……。

source: TEXT_LUCKZG023_03508_MINER03508_000_001<tab>Argh! The supplier will be here soon, and I still haven't finished with my checks! There's no time, no time... I know! If you have a look around the place and see what needs fixing, I'll work out which materials we should order.
target:
TEXT_LUCKZG023_03508_MINER03508_000_001<tab>それゆえ、しっかりと必要な資材を検討したいのだが、
自分独りでは、行商人が来るまでに間に合いそうにない。
すまないが、点検を手伝ってくれないか？

source: TEXT_LUCKZG023_03508_MINER03508_000_002<tab>These traveling peddlers don't hang around, so I've got to have everything ready before she moves on. You'll help the people of Twine, won't you? I knew you would!
target:
TEXT_LUCKZG023_03508_MINER03508_000_002<tab>なに、この町を回って修理した方がいい場所を、
教えてくれるだけでいいんだ。
よろしく頼んだよ。

source: TEXT_LUCKZG023_03508_SYSTEM_000_010<tab>These hinges have seen better days. One good slam and the whole door is liable to fall off.
target:
TEXT_LUCKZG023_03508_SYSTEM_000_010<tab>建物の扉がガタついている……。
修理が必要だろう。

source: TEXT_LUCKZG023_03508_SYSTEM_000_011<tab>There is a deep split in the support beam. If this breaks, the whole building might come down.
target:
TEXT_LUCKZG023_03508_SYSTEM_000_011<tab>柱にヒビが入っている……。
修理が必要だろう。

source: TEXT_LUCKZG023_03508_SYSTEM_000_012<tab>The frame has warped and the door rattles in the breeze.
target:
TEXT_LUCKZG023_03508_SYSTEM_000_012<tab>扉の金具がボロボロだ……。
修理が必要だろう。

source: TEXT_LUCKZG023_03508_MINER03508_000_030<tab>Gods be good, it's worse than I thought...
target: TEXT_LUCKZG023_03508_MINER03508_000_030<tab>……なるほど、修理が必要な場所はそんなにあったか。

TEXT_LUCKZG023_03508_MINER03508_000_031<tab>では、それらの分についても、
資材を発注させてもらおう。

source: TEXT_LUCKZG023_03508_MERCHANT03508_000_032<tab>My, my, the paltry amount I will make from this is hardly worth the effort!
target:
TEXT_LUCKZG023_03508_MERCHANT03508_000_032<tab>採掘が盛んだった頃を知ってる身としては、
これでも発注数が少なくなったと感じるネ。
ギリギリの資材しか買ってくれないネ。

source: TEXT_LUCKZG023_03508_MINER03508_000_033<tab>That's all we can afford at present. Maybe if your prices weren't so extortionate, we'd get a bit more for our gil!
target:
TEXT_LUCKZG023_03508_MINER03508_000_033<tab>今は余裕がないからな。
余分な資材も発注できた昔が羨ましいよ。

source: TEXT_LUCKZG023_03508_MINER03508_000_034<tab>Hmm... This might take a while, but you've played your part. Short on coin though we are, it was worth paying you for your help, considering the amount we'll save from ordering only the bare necessities. You have my thanks.
target:
TEXT_LUCKZG023_03508_MINER03508_000_034<tab>さて、あとは自分と行商人だけで、
資材の見積もりを出すとしよう。
ありがとう、助かったよ。
